(10722, 1, '2016-10-14 09:23:55', '2016-10-14 09:23:55', '[kc_row use_container="yes" column_align="middle" video_bg_url="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dOWFVKb2JqM" _id="557715"][kc_column width="12/12" _id="374767"][kc_column_text _id="261290" css_custom="{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`typography`:{`color|,p`:`#000000`,`font-size|,p`:`18px`}}}}"]\n\nWe are one of America''s leading long-distance moving companies.\n\n[/kc_column_text][kc_column_text _id="500072" css_custom="{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`typography`:{`font-weight|,p`:`300`}}}}"]\n\nPlanning an interstate move? Contact one of our moving experts for a long-distance moving quote. With over 340 agent locations nationwide, United offers convenient long-distance moving packages and premium moving services and to help make your move as simple as possible.\n\n[/kc_column_text][/kc_column][/kc_row][kc_row use_container="yes" _id="847490"][kc_column width="45%" _id="60958"][kc_single_image image_size="full" image_effect_option="__empty__" _id="443984" image_source="media_library" image="10471"][/kc_column][kc_column width="55%" _id="760588"][kc_column_text _id="669682" css_custom="{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`typography`:{`color|,p`:`#000000`,`font-size|,p`:`18px`}}}}"]\n\nLong Distance Moving Quotes\n\n[/kc_column_text][kc_column_text _id="228655" css_custom="{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`typography`:{`font-weight|,p`:`300`}}}}"]\n\nWhen you request a long-distance moving quote from United we will provide an estimate for services that is tailored to fit your budget.\n\nOur professional moving estimators will survey your home to approximate the size size and weight of your load. You''ll subsequently discuss packing, protection and service options to customize a moving package that fits your needs.\n\n[/kc_column_text][/kc_column][/kc_row][kc_row _id="465876"][kc_column width="12/12" _id="694217"][kc_spacing height="30px" _id="66646"][/kc_column][/kc_row][kc_row use_container="yes" _id="140997"][kc_column width="12/12" _id="250259"][kc_column_text _id=