r# width="75%" _id="55110"][kc_tabs active_section="1" _id="737359" type="horizontal_tabs"][kc_tab title="01. our mission" _id="107980"][kc_row_inner## column_align="middle" _id="199591"][kc_column_inner## width="41.66%" _id="809520" css_custom="{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`30px inherit inherit inherit`}}}}"][kc_single_image image_size="full" image_effect_option="__empty__" _id="276197" image_source="media_library" image="10426"][/kc_column_inner##][kc_column_inner## width="58.33%" _id="309567"][kc_column_text _id="929692" css_custom="{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`typography`:{`color|,p`:`#000000`,`font-size|,p`:`18px`}}}}"]\n\nThe mission of us is to continuously strive to exceed our customers&#039; expectations in value and high standard of satisfaction.\n\n[/kc_column_text][kc_column_text _id="482787" css_custom="{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`typography`:{`font-weight|,p`:`300`}}}}"]\n\nWhen it&#039;s time to make a local move, trust us, a local moving company, for the services you want. Since 1948, customers have relied on Atlas for experience, know-how, and affordable moving help. Among local movers, we are known for helping people go new places more easily and more securely. All agents and employees, whether furniture movers or office workers, share this pledge.As a result, every Atlas agent is certified as anJets.\n\n[/kc_column_text][/kc_column_inner##][/kc_row_inner##][/kc_tab][kc_tab title="02. our promise" _id="539549"][kc_row_inner## column_align="middle" _id="270646"][kc_column_inner## width="41.66%" _id="949460" css_custom="{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`30px inherit inherit inherit`}}}}"][kc_single_image image_size="full" image_effect_option="__empty__" _id="380930" image_source="media_library" image="11074"][/kc_column_inner##][kc_column_inner## width="58.33%" _id="467004"][kc_column_text _id="675339" css_custom="{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`typography`:{`color|,p`:`#000000`,`font-size|,p`:`18px`}}}}"]\n\nLily tried to be helpful. Estimate was way off and I didn&#039;t appreciate being told what the gratuity should be..\n\n[/kc_column_text][kc_column_text _id="253126" css_custom="{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`typography`:{`font-weight|,p`:`300`}}}}"]\n\nMoving truck took too long to arrive from NY to CA. Furniture (bookcases, large roll top desk, armoire, very large mirror etc.) received in damaged condition, baseball sized hole in top of armoire. NOT happy with this move at all as delivery was LATE, items were broken and we&#039;re still going through the boxes to check for more damage.Would not recommend this moving company to anyone!! I could go on, but I would be reiterating. Lily tried to be helpful.\n\n[/kc_column_text][/kc_column_inner##][/kc_row_inner##][/kc_tab][kc_tab title="03. core values" _id="382623"][kc_row_inner## column_align="middle" _id="862547"][kc_column_inner## width="41.66%" _id="615450" css_custom="{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`30px inherit inherit inherit`}}}}"][kc_single_image image_size="full" image_effect_option="__empty__" _id="527319" image_source="media_library" image="11075"][/kc_column_inner##][kc_column_inner## width="58.33%" _id="324635"][kc_column_text _id="191057" css_custom="{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`typography`:{`color|,p`:`#000000`,`font-size|,p`:`18px`}}}}"]\n\nMy goods are been held hostage for payment,.The sales person was pleasant and helpful, the others are insouciant.\n\n[/kc_column_text][kc_column_text _id="338900" css_custom="{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`typography`:{`font-weight|,p`:`300`}}}}"]\n\nJets rude driver Miha Gulscinschi refused to deliver my goods after five days delay, claiming he cannot back up a trailer into a storage company yard in Naples, he demanded $500 for redelivery.\nHis operations manager back the demand for the $500.Would not recommend this moving company to anyone!! I could go on, but I would be reiterating.The sales person was pleasant and helpful, the others are insouciant.\n\n[/kc_column_text][/kc_column_inner##][/kc_row_inner##][/kc_tab][/kc_tabs][/kc_column_inner#][kc_column_inner# width="25%" _id="972055"][kc_single_image image_size="full" image_effect_option="yes" _id="227313" image_source="media_library" image="10425" image_effect="effect-v1" on_click_action="open_custom_link" custom_link="http://localhost/pts_wp_demo/wp_jets/about-us/||"][/kc_column_inner#][/kc_row_inner#][/kc_column_inner][/kc_row_inner][/kc_column][/kc_row]', 'Home 2', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '9909-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-05-17 11:58:15', '2017-05-17 11:58:15', '', 9909, 'http://localhost/wpmoverdeal/?p=11210', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
