(11215, 1, '2017-05-12 11:34:27', '2017-05-12 11:34:27', '<style type="text/css"></style><section class="kc-elm kc-css-696966 kc_row"><div class="kc-row-container  kc-container"><div class="kc-wrap-columns"><div class="kc-elm kc-css-94018 kc_col-sm-12 kc_column kc_col-sm-12"><div class="kc-col-container"><div class="kc-elm kc-css-809857 kc_text_block test-pic-desc"><h4><strong>Highly recommended</strong></h4>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>Delhi to Indore</h4>\n<p>I not being a tech savvy was hesitant in availing <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#">Read More</a>shifting services of online site. However, my worries quickly vanished when I came across Moverdeal. It was so easy to place the details of my shifting requirement through their user friendly web site. The experience was even more enhanced with the regular updates about the bidding from multiple movers &amp; packers, on my shifting through regular emails and SMS. I was always aware of the latest bids, which helped me to choose the best mover &amp; packer with the best rate. All the best.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></section>', 'Prithviraj Datta', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'prithviraj-datta', '', '', '2017-05-12 11:36:13', '2017-05-12 11:36:13', '[kc_row use_container="yes" _id="696966"][kc_column width="12/12" video_bg_url="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dOWFVKb2JqM" _id="94018"][kc_column_text _id="809857" class="test-pic-desc"]\r\n<h4><strong>Highly recommended</strong></h4>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4>Delhi to Indore</h4>\r\nI not being a tech savvy was hesitant in availing <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#">Read More</a>shifting services of online site. However, my worries quickly vanished when I came across Moverdeal. It was so easy to place the details of my shifting requirement through their user friendly web site. The experience was even more enhanced with the regular updates about the bidding from multiple movers &amp; packers, on my shifting through regular emails and SMS. I was always aware of the